b_{i}P^{\sigma}\frac{Y}{A}p_{i}^{-\sigma} & \leq & z_{i}k\left(\frac{1}{2\chi}\frac{\alpha}{1-\alpha}w\right)^{-\left(1-\alpha\right)}\\
