\end_inset

 Realized revenues are
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{eqnarray*}
\pi\left(b_{i},z_{i},A,k,p\right) & = & \begin{cases}
py^{d}-C_{u}\left(y^{d}\right) & \mbox{if }b_{i}\leq\hat{\bar{b}}\\
py^{d}-C_{c}\left(y^{d}\right) & \mbox{if }\hat{\bar{b}}<b_{i}\leq\bar{b}_{\mbox{case2}}\\
